Sure, here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "srediću":

1. *Srediću* sobu pre večere. (I will tidy up the room before dinner.)
2. Kada *središ* sobu, možeš da ideš napolje. (When you tidy up the room, you can go outside.)
3. Ona mi je rekla da će *srediti* sve za nas. (She told me she would arrange everything for us.)
4. Ja ću *srediti* račune danas popodne. (I will settle the bills this afternoon.)
5. Ako mi *središ* torbu, biću ti veoma zahvalan. (If you organize my bag for me, I'll be very grateful.)
6. Moram *da sredim* svoje misli pre nego što donesem odluku. (I need to sort out my thoughts before making a decision.)
7. Da li si *sredio* stvari za putovanje? (Did you sort out everything for the trip?)
8. *Sredio bih* neke stvari na poslu pre nego što idem na odmor. (I would take care of some things at work before going on vacation.)